---
import GlobalLayout from "../../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro";
---

<GlobalLayout class:list={["bg-white"]}>
    <div class="ellipse-left"></div>
    <div class="ellipse-right"></div>
    
    <article class="flex flex-col items-center py-16">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-9xl px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-[Noto_Serif_Display] text-[#004346] mb-6 leading-tight">
                    Beyond Groceries – How Super-Apps Like Daily Bazzar Can Redefine Daily Living in the Northeast
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#204040] mb-6 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                    Daily Bazzar is redefining everyday living in Northeast India by evolving into a super-app—bringing groceries, medicines, and services together in one trusted, hyperlocal digital platform.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-[#204040]/70 mb-6">
                    <span>September 09, 2025</span>
                    <span class="hidden sm:inline">•</span>
                    <span>By Daily Bazzar Team</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
                    <span class="bg-[#F0F2F4] text-[#0094BD] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Super-App Northeast India</span>
                    <span class="bg-[#F0F2F4] text-[#0094BD] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">DailyBazzar Services</span>
                    <span class="bg-[#F0F2F4] text-[#0094BD] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">One-Stop Digital Platform Assam</span>
                    <span class="bg-[#F0F2F4] text-[#0094BD] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Online Groceries and Services Jorhat</span>
                    <span class="bg-[#F0F2F4] text-[#0094BD] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Hyperlocal Super-App.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-9xl px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
            <div class="bg-[#fafdff] rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-[#e6faff] p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12">
                <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#204040]">
                    <h2>Introduction</h2>
                    <p>Imagine an app where you can order groceries, book a plumber, schedule medicine delivery, and even hire a driver—all in one place. That’s the power of a super-app. While the concept is popular in markets like China (WeChat) and Southeast Asia (Grab, Gojek), India is still in the early stages.
</p>

                    <p>For the <strong>Northeast region</strong>, where access to diverse services is limited, a <strong>super-app like DailyBazzar</strong> could completely redefine daily living.
</p>

                    <h2>What is a Super-App?</h2>

                    <p>A <strong>super-app</strong> is a single digital platform offering multiple services—shopping, payments, deliveries, bookings, and more. Instead of juggling 10 different apps, customers rely on one.
</p>
                    <h2>Why the Northeast Needs a Super-App</h2>

                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>1. Limited Access to Services:</strong>
                         Many towns don’t have platforms for groceries, medicines, and household services.
</li>
                        <li><strong>2. Digital Growth:</strong>
                         With rising smartphone penetration, people are ready for all-in-one solutions.</li>
                        <li><strong>3. Support for Local Economy:</strong>
                          A super-app that onboards local vendors and service providers ensures money stays within the community.</li>
                        
                    </ol>

                    <h2>DailyBazzar’s Roadmap Toward a Super-App</h2>
                    
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Groceries & Essentials:</strong> Fresh produce, meat, fish, bakery items.</li>
                        <li><strong>Medicines:</strong> Prescription-based, safe, and compliant deliveries.</li>
                        <li><strong>Household Services:</strong> Caretakers, electricians, plumbers, drivers.</li>
                        <li><strong>Future Add-ons:</strong> Digital payments, ride-hailing, and more.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p>This <strong>multi-service ecosystem</strong> ensures DailyBazzar is not just a shopping app—it’s a <strong>lifestyle platform</strong> for the Northeast.
</p>

                    <h2>Benefits for Customers</h2>
                   
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Convenience:</strong> Everything in one place
</li>
                        <li><strong>Affordability:</strong>  Competitive pricing with local vendors</li>
                        <li><strong>Trust:</strong> Verified service providers and shopsnd more.</li>
                        <li><strong>Community Growth:</strong> Local businesses and workers gain more opportunities</li>
                    </ol>
                    <h2>Conclusion</h2>

                    <p>The next wave of digital commerce in the Northeast isn’t just about <strong>buying groceries online—</strong>it’s about creating a <strong>super-app ecosystem</strong> that improves daily living. With its focus on <strong>local vendors, hyperlocal delivery, and multiple services, DailyBazzar is on the path to becoming the region’s first true super-app</strong>.
                    
                        
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Navigation Section -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 mt-16">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 p-6 bg-[#fafdff] rounded-xl border border-[#e6faff]">
